Definition: shrubby tree widely distributed along tropical shores
Example: yields a light tough wood used for canoe outriggers and a fiber used for cordage and caulk; often cultivated for ornament
Synonyms: majagua, mahagua, balibago, purau, Hibiscus_tiliaceus, hibiscus, shrubby, tree, widely, distributed, along, tropical, shores, yields, a, light, tough, wood, used, for, canoe, outriggers, and, fiber, cordage, caulk, often, cultivated, ornament
Category: noun.plant
